Melissa,Data,creates,data,quality,and,address,management,solutions,for,websites,and,businesses,Their,services,standardize,verify,and,enhance,global,contact,data,including,addresses,phone,numbers,and,email,addresses,The,Melissa,Data,Name,Object,API,allows,customer,applications,to,parse,names,into,distinct,components,and,indicate,gender,The,API,is,also,capable,of,screening,names,for,possible,vulgar,words,fake,names,and,company,names,as,well,as,create,salutations,based,on,parsed,information